      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-long-does-it-take-to-launch-a-blog"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>A basic blog takes 1–2 weeks to set up. A fully optimized blog with 10 posts takes 4–6 weeks. The technical setup is fast. Content creation takes time. Do not rush the content.</p></div></div>
  </div>
