      <span class="faq-q-text">Do I need to know coding to launch a blog?</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="do-i-need-to-know-coding-to-launch-a-blog"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. WordPress and modern page builders let you create a professional blog without writing code. Basic HTML helps for formatting, but it is not required. Focus on content and marketing. Technical skills can come later.</p></div></div>
  </div>
