      <span class="faq-q-text">How much does it cost to launch a blog?</span>
      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="how-much-does-it-cost-to-launch-a-blog"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Minimum viable: $100–$200 for domain, hosting, and a premium theme for one year. Professional setup: $500–$1,000 including tools, plugins, and design assets. Ongoing costs: $20–$100 per month for hosting, email, and tools.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
