      <span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span>
    </button>
    <div class="faq-a" id="should-i-use-ai-to-write-my-blog-posts"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>AI can help with research, outlines, and first drafts. Do not publish raw AI output. Edit for accuracy, voice, and depth. Google does not penalize AI content. It penalizes low-quality content, regardless of how it was written.</p></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
