    <div class="faq-a" id="what-is-the-most-important-thing-to-focus-on-in-th"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Consistency. Publish on schedule. Promote every post. Respond to comments and emails. Build the habit of creating and sharing content. Everything else is secondary in month one.</p></div></div>
